.B int array
;  (* Histogram of bucket sizes\&.  This array 
.B histo
has
length 
.B max_bucket_length + 1
\&.  The value of
.B histo\&.(i)
is the number of buckets whose size is 
.B i
\&. *) 
 }

.sp

.sp

.I val stats 
: 
.B ('a, 'b) t -> statistics
.sp

.B Hashtbl\&.stats tbl
returns statistics about the table 
.B tbl
:
number of buckets, size of the biggest bucket, distribution of
buckets by size\&.
.sp
.B "Since"
4.00.0
.sp

